   Android: Settings > Google > Ads > Delete advertising ID or opt out of ads personalization.

2. Usage Data
   We may collect non-personally identifiable usage data such as app interactions, session duration, and crash reports solely to improve App stability and performance.

We do NOT collect:
- Your name, email address, or phone number
- Location data
- Health or fitness data
- Financial information
